                <note rend="inline" type="source">835.73/158: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Argentina</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Riddle</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-08-21T15:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 21, 1922—3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>41. Your August 11, 7 p.m.</p>
                <p>It will be a source of great satisfaction to me personally, if, before my
                    departure from Washington Wednesday next, I should be in a <pb facs="0657"
                        n="537" xml:id="pg_537"/> position to announce definitely the opening of
                    this additional means of communication with the countries of South America.</p>
                <p>Please see the Minister for Foreign Affairs, advise him of the foregoing,
                    emphasize my personal interest, and express the hope that he may find it
                    possible to give the promised confirmation which would be most gratifying to
                    this Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
